==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Livable
<hw>Liv"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Such as
can be lived.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Such as is pleasant to live in; fit or suitable to
live in.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A more delightful or <qex>livable</qex> region is not easily to be
found.</q> <rj><qau>T. Arnold.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Live</ent>⟦br⟧
